{"word":"ἀπόθετος","slug":"ἀπόθετος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπόθετος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀποτίθημι'><el>ἀποτίθημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>laid by, stored up</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>hidden, secret, mysterious</i>, <el>ἔπη</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>reserved for occasions, special</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}